# Session transcripts

Do not read `documentation/session-transcripts/` unless the user names a specific file (path or @-mention).

Transcripts are task handover material, not PACS authority. Normative source is `standard/`. When a handover conflicts with `standard/` or the working tree, follow `standard/` and the tree.

Do not browse, grep, or search this folder for background context.
